   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Through sitologoi: Arabikos, son of Ptollas, has shifted, for the crop of year 18 and 17 and 10, four donkeys of wheat, equal 4 donkeys. Year 18 and 17 and 10, between Pauni 27 and Epeiph 8.</ab>
